{
  "stem": "8233.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But she-- I-- like I say, I don't know if she knew that my father was dead or not, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But she had that will, that strong will.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She said no, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In Yiddish she used to talk to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No, my [NON-ENGLISH], please, [NON-ENGLISH]-- she would call me [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Please, you're going to see.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We're going to survive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We're going to survive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We have to tell people what-- [SOBBING] what's going on and what happened.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I couldn't leave it alone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I wouldn't go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so I stayed for her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[SOBBING] And that's how we stayed in camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And very often when we used to go to work, a young fellow would-- a SS.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that was before.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I forgot.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That was before.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They would-- they would have dogs with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they would just make fun.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Like, there was a river.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They would throw in straw into the river and would tell the girls that did not know how to swim, go and get it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they will just laugh.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they would take the gun and shoot in the air just to scare us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Because the girls wouldn't want to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We wouldn't want to go into that water.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So he would take the gun and he'd-- and they were laughing and laughing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They were having so much fun.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I just don't know how human beings can do that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's what I was saying to my mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What for, and what for?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[SOBBING] German or not German, it didn't matter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A, a person is a person.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[SOBBING] I'd say, how-- it's, it's just unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
